scopecontent.p:
The collection includes three bound ledgers, one with a cover, as well as four loose ledger
        pages. The ledger numbered 48.663 contains a listing of receipts from July 1, 1901 to July
        1, 1906. Categories include Acts 1862, 1890 and special Appropriations; Incidentals;
        Creamery; Farm; Garden; Electric Lights; Shops; Laundry; Mess; Uniform; Fees; Text Books;
        and Total. The names listed appear to include both faculty and students.
